Package environment.GUI.views

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Animated.Visual
    The interface used to produce the visual representation of the Location.
    SimulatorView<T>
    The SimulatorView interface is used by classes which deliver information about the status of the simulation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animated
    The Animated class is a subclass of the JFrame which implements the SimulatorView interface.
    Animated.AnimationPanel
    The AnimationaPanel class is a subclass of the JPanel class which is designed for drawing visual representations of the Station objects.
    CommandLine
    The CommandLine class displays information of the simulation via the Console (System.out).
    Graph
    A graphical view of the simulation.
    TestCommandLine  
    TestGraph  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Animated.Visualisation
    The Animated.Visualisation enumeration contains visual representations of objects to be displayed in the Animated.AnimationPanel.
    Graph.StatisticType
    All the values and encapsulated functionality of the elements that will be added to the Graph.statisticTypes.
    Graph.VehicleType
    All the values and encapsulated functionality of the elements that will be added to the Graph.vehicleTypes.
